<TITLE>EXOVIR &lt;XOVR.O> TO BUYBACK SHARES</TITLE>
<DATELINE>    GREAT NECK, N.Y., Oct 20 - </DATELINE><BODY>Exovir Inc said its board
authorized the purchase of up to one mln dlrs of its common
stock.
    The dollar amount represents approximately 120,000 shares,
the company said. Exovir has about three mln common shares
outstanding.
    The company said it believed its stock was substantially
undervalued.
